&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>You take a photograph of a bird, &lt;br>
data is in your camera and the bird has flown. &lt;br>
You take a photograph of a river, &lt;br>
data is in your camera, and the water has gone away. &lt;br>
You listen to a music performance, music is recorded. &lt;br>
Data is on the storage device but the musician has gone. &lt;br>
You smell a breeze coming from a flower, &lt;br>
you experienced the smell but the flower is far away.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>